lead_paragraph: Phelps roared from last to first on the final lap to win the 100-meter freestyle against his rival Ryan Lochte in the Arena Pro Swim Series meet in Mesa, Ariz.

abstract: Michael Phelps wins 100-meter freestyle in Arena Pro Swim Series meet in Arizona.
